user.biography: The GPU, our invention, is the engine of computer graphics and GPU deep learning has ignited modern AI — the next era of computing.

node.text:
Now is a great time to build your career as a #developer or technologist. We've got an essential learning series in #AI, robotics, deep learning, and accelerated graphics to get you on your way.

Go to our AI Essentials highlight and story to access this series.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NVIDIA on July 12, 2021 tagging @paloaltontwks.

node.text:
Cybercrime cost the American public more than $4 billion in reported losses over the course of 2020, according to the FBI. To stay ahead of emerging threats, Palo Alto Networks, a global cybersecurity leader, has developed the first virtual next-generation firewall (NGFW) designed to be accelerated by NVIDIA’s BlueField data processing unit (DPU).

Learn more in our Firewall highlight and story.

The latest #NVIDIARTX laptop GPUs are powered by the NVIDIA Ampere architecture, bringing next-gen creative power to designers, engineers, and data scientists working remotely.

Learn more in our RTX Laptops story and highlight.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NVIDIA on July 07, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text:
Introducing our “first big bet” on the #digitalbiology revolution, our CEO Jensen Huang unveiled Cambridge-1, the U.K.’s most powerful supercomputer that promises to harness partnerships across the U.K. for breakthroughs with a “global impact.”

Learn more in our Cambridge-1 highlight and story.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NVIDIA on July 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'nVIDIA SPECIAL ADDRESS Supercharging healthcare research on Cambridge-1 Jul7 3p.m. CET I a.m. PT JENSEN HUANG CEO & Founder, NVIDIA'.

node.text:
On July 7, watch our CEO and founder, Jensen Huang, deliver a special address for the unveiling of #NVIDIACambridge1, the UK's fastest supercomputer. 

View our story or highlight to save the date.
nvidia.com/healthcare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NVIDIA on June 30, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text:
We are partnering with Google Cloud to create the industry’s first AI-on-5G lab to speed AI application development for 5G network operators. 

Learn more: nvidia.com/mwc

To accelerate the new era of industrial #AI and #HPC, we are announcing the addition of new technologies to the NVIDIA HGX AI supercomputing platform, making supercomputing more useful to a growing number of industries.

Learn more in our HGX story and highlight.

Just announced: We're supporting @Arm-based CPUs in the NVIDIA Aerial A100 AI-on-5G platform, enabling enterprises to deploy intelligent services over software-defined, cloud-native #5G vRAN.

Learn more: nvidia.com/mwc

node.text:
Harness the power of #AI to quickly turn simple brushstrokes into realistic landscape images for backgrounds, concept exploration, or creative inspiration.

The NVIDIA Canvas app lets you create as quickly as you can imagine. Learn more and try the open beta (link in our story and highlight), and follow @NVIDIACreators for more from NVIDIA Studio, a program that provides creators with hardware and software tools to assist in realizing their creative visions.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by NVIDIA on June 22, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, television and screen.

node.text:
NVIDIA AI LaunchPad brings AI within reach for every enterprise. Build, deploy, and scale #AI projects with access to world-class facilities and industry-leading technology.

Learn more from our "AI LaunchPad" Highlight and Instagram Story.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NVIDIA on June 15, 2021 tagging @nvidiaembedded.

node.text:
Announcing the new NVIDIA Jetson AGX Xavier Industrial. It brings unbeatable performance to all your #AI embedded #industrial and functional safety applications in a power-efficient, rugged form-factor.  Designed to Perform. Built to Last.

Learn more about embedded systems with Jetson: nvidia.com/jetson

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NVIDIA on June 09, 2021 tagging @nvidiaomniverse. May be an image of map.

node.text:
#NVIDIAOmniverse is a revolutionary virtual platform built for collaboration and real-time true-to-reality simulation. Project teams can now connect every phase of their process—from ideation & conceptual design to production automation on the factory floor. 

Learn more  at @NVIDIAOmniverse.
